  #main_panel_inner.columns

    #left_content
      %h1.emphasis CAN WE QUOTE YOU HAPPY?
      %p.emphasis With outstanding service, flexible terms and low rates - we know we can!
      %p We would love to provide you with a quote for cleaning your business premises. Please call us on 01603 783800 (or 07790 306047) to arrange a good time for us to visit.
